fix: robust Qwen3.5 text-only compat for GRPO training

Root cause: compute_3d_position_ids kept stale rope_deltas from generation
step, causing RuntimeError during logprob computation when inputs_embeds=None.

Three-level defense:
1. Class-level patch: unconditionally clear rope_deltas before calling
   original compute_3d_position_ids; catch RuntimeError and fall back to 1D
2. Instance-level hook: register_forward_pre_hook clears rope_deltas
3. ClearRopeDeltasCallback: defense-in-depth for all trainer scripts

Applied to all 7 scripts: train_grpo_sweep, train_grpo_halluzero,
eval_phase_point, eval_halluzero, analyze_gradients, run_curriculum_strategies.
